# ============================================================
# Explicit LCSC component definitions
# EXP_012 ESP32 Motor Controller
#
# NOTE: mpn MUST be the LCSC part number (not manufacturer PN).
# Atopile maps mpn → BOM "LCSC" column for JLCPCB.
# ============================================================

# ── Resistors (0603) ─────────────────────────────────────────

